      "message": "Patch Set 9:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el5/x86_64, el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/8027d8a2-9ab4-11e1-96af-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
